descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the official Gospel Broadcasting Network application for your mobile device!

Check out all kinds of content that interests you. After you’ve downloaded and enjoyed the content, you can share it with your friends via Twitter, Facebook, or email.

For more information about GBN, please visit: http://www.gbntv.org

The GBN app was developed with the Subsplash App Platform.

descriptionShort: Official app for the Gospel Broadcasting Network

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- We've consolidated Listen and Watch into a single Play button on the media player. Users can still switch between listening and watching modes.
- If enabled, Messaging now features an option to silence all notifications for a predetermined period of time.
- You can now start Picture-in-picture playback in the player to watch video and browse the app at the same time.
- Misc. bug fixes and improvements.
